Package: scregclust
Title: Reconstructing the regulatory programs of target genes in single cell data
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ida", "Larsson", ,"ida.larsson@igp.uu.se", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5422-4243")),
    person("Felix", "Held", ,"felix.held@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7679-7752")),
    person("Sven", "Nelander", ,"sven.nelander@igp.uu.se", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1758-1262")))
Description: This package provides an implementation of our scRegClust
  algorithm (Larsson, Held, et al., 2023, <doi:10.1101/2023.03.10.532041>)
  which aims to reconstruct the regulatory programs of target genes in single cell data.
  Target genes are clustered and each cluster is associated with a linear
  model accounting for the regulatory program driving the genes in the cluster.
